regen.absent_element: mechanism for handling inconsistencies or errors in case records during updates
regen.new_specification: The system should have a mechanism to handle and resolve inconsistencies or errors that arise during the manual or automatic update of case record statuses.

regen.absent_element: mechanism for handling conflicts or inconsistencies in case records due to changes in case definitions
regen.new_specification: The system shall provide a mechanism to resolve conflicts or inconsistencies in case records that arise from changes in case definitions.
The system shall implement reusable questionnaire libraries using common terminology to support case investigation.

label: Systems supporting OM must provide the ability to publish investigation specific questionnaires and implementation guides.
